{"tid":1802781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過突然間好掛住一個人","createTime":"2019-12-29T17:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:42:26.000Z","uid":320761,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2e89921422f8d971299fb3d6947a2cfb689c1c11","tid":1802781,"uid":320761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"明明對方已經狠狠地離開咗<br />\n明明我已經進步咗認清事實<br />\n明明我知道所有野都返唔到轉頭<br />\n明明我已經諗少咗佢好多 <br />\n幾個月以嚟 好似差唔多可以放低佢 唔會再特登偷睇佢ig<br />\n<br />\n琴日無啦啦勾返起啲回憶 然後越諗越多 諗返起所有一點一滴 都仲係好似琴日發生嘅事咁<br />\n諗起我地勾過手指尾話會結婚<br />\n諗起我地24小時由朝對到晚<br />\n諗起陪你係醫院過咗一晚<br />\n多美好<br />\n<br />\n突然間 又好掛住佢<br />\n<br />\n原來 放低一個人 真係唔是咁易的<br />\n而佢 一早已經有新嘅生活<br />\n得我仲原地踏步<br />\n<br />\n肥妹 突然好想你 你會在哪裏<br />\n<br />\n求圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c2e670ef9fb33cfa07f44ff2cf8244da487ea2","tid":1802781,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK90YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=85f7a320\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f39173ee6620b1cfebcbcf6dce45464d6822d5f6","tid":1802781,"uid":241250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a340c3081487422b0e7516fe94855369f9515b1","tid":1802781,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"8ecf57afd6ef444d14065ec18477afd734c19cb2","tid":1802781,"uid":339216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"s